																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">4</div> <div class="vers-content">For even when we were with you, we foretold you that we should suffer tribulations, as also it is come to pass, and you know.</div></div></td>
																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">4</div> <div class="vers-content">Indeed, when we visited you we told you that trials were to befall us; now you can see for yourselves that it was true.</div></div></td>
								</tr><tr>									<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">5</div> <div class="vers-content">Propterea et ego amplius non sustinens, misi ad cognoscendam fidem vestram: ne forte tentaverit vos is qui tentat, et inanis fiat labor noster.</div></div></td>
																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">5</div> <div class="vers-content">For this cause also, I, forbearing no longer, sent to know your faith: lest perhaps he that tempteth should have tempted you, and our labour should be made vain.</div></div></td>
																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">5</div> <div class="vers-content">That was my reason for sending him, when I could bear it no longer, to make sure of your faith; it might be that the tempter of souls had been tempting you, and that all our labour would go for nothing.</div></div></td>
								</tr><tr>									<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">6</div> <div class="vers-content">Nunc autem veniente Timotheo ad nos a vobis, et annuntiante nobis fidem et caritatem vestram, et quia memoriam nostri habetis bonam semper, desiderantes nos videre, sicut et nos quoque vos:</div></div></td>
																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">6</div> <div class="vers-content">But now when Timothy came to us from you, and related to us your faith and charity, and that you have a good remembrance of us always, desiring to see us as we also to see you;</div></div></td>
																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">6</div> <div class="vers-content">Now that Timothy has come back to us from seeing you, and told us about your faith and love, and the kind remembrance you have of us all the while, longing for our company as we long for yours,</div></div></td>
