																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">7</div> <div class="vers-content">Therefore we were comforted, brethren, in you, in all our necessity and tribulation, by your faith,</div></div></td>
																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">7</div> <div class="vers-content">your faith has brought us comfort, brethren, amidst all our difficulties and trials.</div></div></td>
