																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">8</div> <div class="vers-content">If only you stand firm in the Lord, it brings fresh life to us.</div></div></td>
								</tr><tr>									<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">9</div> <div class="vers-content">Quam enim gratiarum actionem possumus Deo retribuere pro vobis in omni gaudio, quo gaudemus propter vos ante Deum nostrum,</div></div></td>
																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">9</div> <div class="vers-content">For what thanks can we return to God for you, in all the joy wherewith we rejoice for you before our God,</div></div></td>
																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">9</div> <div class="vers-content">What thanks can we return to God for you, to express all the joy we feel in rejoicing over you in the presence of our God,</div></div></td>
