																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">10</div> <div class="vers-content">Night and day more abundantly praying that we may see your face, and may accomplish those things that are wanting to your faith?</div></div></td>
																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">10</div> <div class="vers-content">as we pray more than ever, night and day, for the opportunity of seeing you face to face, and making good whatever your faith still lacks?</div></div></td>
								</tr><tr>									<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">11</div> <div class="vers-content">Ipse autem Deus, et Pater noster, et Dominus noster Jesus Christus, dirigat viam nostram ad vos.</div></div></td>
																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">11</div> <div class="vers-content">Now God himself and our Father, and our Lord Jesus Christ, direct our way unto you.</div></div></td>
