																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">12</div> <div class="vers-content">And may the Lord multiply you, and make you abound in charity towards one another, and towards all men: as we do also towards you,</div></div></td>
																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">12</div> <div class="vers-content">and as for you, may the Lord give you a rich and an ever richer love for one another and for all men, like ours for you.</div></div></td>
